Beiersdorf to Raise Female Top Manager Quota, Abendblatt Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-10-18T07:04:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/beiersdorf-to-raise-female-top-manager-quota-abendblatt-says.html
Beiersdorf AG (BEI) , the only Hamburg-
based company on Germany’s benchmark DAX Index, plans to
increase the number of top female managers to between 25 and 30
percent by 2020,  Hamburger Abendblatt  reported today, citing
Rolf Lange, the company’s human resources spokesman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  